metadata.name: The Community Pillar
metadata.description:
" United we stand, divided we fall "  
This art is about the bond between artists & collectors in NFT World .This is a special relationship which have been born since art came alive.Thank you & well done for staying in victorious  bull market & defeated bear market .We are Strong,We are One.  
United we stand ,divided we fall.


Artists & Collectors  
Can't be separated .

Abstract work inspired by the love of NFT community  
Happy 2023.
